IMPLEMENTATION ROADMAP

Phase 1: Foundation (Months 1-6)

· Current state assessment and baseline establishment
· Stallion core transformation team formation
· Ant-inspired optimization pilot programs
· Crow intelligence market analysis platform

Phase 2: Core Transformation (Months 6-18)

· Legacy system modernization execution
· Cloud migration and platform implementation
· Data and AI foundation establishment
· Security transformation implementation

Phase 3: Optimization & Innovation (Months 18-36)

· Distributed optimization network deployment
· Continuous improvement culture establishment
· Innovation pipeline development
· Digital product development capability

Phase 4: Sustained Transformation (Months 36+)

· Self-evolving enterprise capability
· Market leadership through continuous innovation
· Ecosystem partnership development
· Digital business model dominance

